Package: cdmAcm0018
Title: Implementation of CDM Large-Scale Methodology ACM0018
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Christiaan", family = "Pauw", email = "christiaan.pauw@gmal.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides tidyverse-aligned tooling to implement the Clean Development Mechanism
    large-scale methodology ACM0018 "Electricity generation from biomass in power-only plants".
    Functions translate numbered equations, applicability conditions, and calculation workflows
    into reproducible R code and include simulation utilities for demonstration and testing
    purposes tailored to biomass-fired power generation facilities.
